{"TopicId":203704,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Fix Lag On Linux Mint [NVIDIA USERS ONLY] [i guess]","CreatedByName":"kindertux","CreatedById":212681,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-08T21:39:36Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"kindertux","CreatedById":212681,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-08T21:39:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi, You\u0027re Probably Here Because Your KSP Is Laging, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFollow This To Fix Lag:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMenu \u0026gt; System Config \u0026gt; Administration \u0026gt; Driver manager \u0026gt; Put Your Password.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis Screen Will Show You The Available Drives For \u0022Download\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmy GPU is a GeForce GT 520\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ESelect\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E: Recommended\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EExample Image:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022713123228.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002267.27\u0022 height=\u0022337\u0022 width=\u0022501\u0022 src=\u0022https://miracleplus.weebly.com/uploads/1/2/5/0/125047053/713123228.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter Selecting, Click \u0022Apply Changes\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter Installing The Driver, A Message Will Appear Telling You To Restart Your Computer, Click \u0022Restart Now\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter That Open KSP, And Play Without Interruptions \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#e74c3c;\u0022\u003EIf You Have Problems Installing Drivers, Read This Article:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://linuxconfig.org/how-to-install-nvidia-drivers-on-linux-mint\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://linuxconfig.org/how-to-install-nvidia-drivers-on-linux-mint \u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002200e4257db0b2a280a6698877a6b2941b--linux-\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002231.86\u0022 height=\u0022151\u0022 width=\u0022474\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.pinimg.com/474x/00/e4/25/00e4257db0b2a280a6698877a6b2941b--linux-mint-note.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGoodBye!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}